{
  "stem": "11964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had a number of neighbors who obviously were warned about the action, and they got there much earlier than we did.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say there were probably between 20 to 30 people there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a young child there, which was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] very annoying to very many people, unfortunately, because everybody was worried that he would cry and make noises.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we persevered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really don't remember how many days we were there, but I do remember the anxiety and the trauma that we were going through because we were certain that our parents had not been warned, and we just didn't know what would have been happening to them.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, when we left the attic, we found out the worst.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our parents have been taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Our parents have been taken away with all these people who unexpectedly found themselves totally open to the raids.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could not find out what happened to them, where they were taken.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Except the following morning, after we came out, a man from the Judenrat came up to us and presented us with two things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One was my father's silver cigarette case, which he had had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the sil-- the cigarette case had his and my mother's signatures in gold duplicated, and he had the names of all three of us in gold encrusted there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But these were removed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just the case was returned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And a little gold medallion from my mother in which there was a little piece of paper, where my mother wrote to us a note saying, dear children, we are so sorry this is happening to us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Whatever you do, make sure you stay together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Take care of yourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
